702149f-a.text:
White Plains Road, at Burke Ave., showing the elevated station of the I.R.T. White Plains Road subway line. The frame houses, seen on the right, are on the north side of Burke Ave., extending from White
Plains Road to Cruger Ave.
About 1917.
James Suydam.
